Package jetbrains.mps.generator.runtime

Interface TemplateCallSite

  • public interface TemplateCallSite
    Instance of a particular location in a template that delegates execution flow to another template. Generally a $CALL$ or a rule consequence with a reference to a template. Gives a level of indirection when invoking templates to better control/augment what's going on along with template processing.
    Since:
    2019.3
